{"data": [{"id": "4745454", "title": "Nvidia's Sellers May Be Missing The Big Picture", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/502379459/image_502379459.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Nvidia World Headquarters\" data-id=\"502379459\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5616px\" height=\"3744px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/502379459/image_502379459.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/502379459/image_502379459.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/502379459/image_502379459.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/502379459/image_502379459.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/502379459/image_502379459.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/502379459/image_502379459.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/502379459/image_502379459.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/502379459/image_502379459.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">JasonDoiy</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I built a strong position in NVIDIA (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NVDA\" title=\"NVIDIA Corporation\">NVDA</a></span>) when the most prominent generative AI tool so far (ChatGPT) was first introduced to the mass public (at the end of 2022). Since then, I've been very bullish on NVIDIA and have regularly added</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/502379459/image_502379459.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745454-nvidias-sellers-fail-to-see-the-big-picture", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 03:32:10"}, {"id": "4745460", "title": "Stagflation Fears And Soaring U.S. Yields: S&P 500's Next Move", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business Planning\" data-id=\"175599141\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5616px\" height=\"3744px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">blackred</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Zain Vawda</em></p> <h2><strong>FOMC Reaction and Implications</strong></h2> <p>Yesterday\u2019s significant selloff was inspired by the Fed shifting to a hawkish outlook for 2025. They now plan for only two small rate cuts totaling 0.5% during the year.</p> <p>This change</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745460-stagflation-fears-and-soaring-us-yields-s-and-p-500-next-move", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 03:20:00"}, {"id": "4745461", "title": "FactSet Research Systems Inc. 2025 Q1 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by FactSet Research Systems Inc. in conjunction with their 2025 Q1 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106254\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745461-factset-research-systems-inc-2025-q1-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 03:10:26"}, {"id": "4745450", "title": "Procter & Gamble: Inventory Does Not Lie And Points To Hold", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157198425/image_157198425.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"pinocchio superliar\" data-id=\"157198425\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1202px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157198425/image_157198425.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157198425/image_157198425.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157198425/image_157198425.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157198425/image_157198425.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157198425/image_157198425.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157198425/image_157198425.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157198425/image_157198425.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157198425/image_157198425.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">THEPALMER</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>PG Stock: Previous Thesis and 2025 FYQ1 Recap</h2> <p>I last analyzed <strong>Procter &amp; Gamble</strong> stock (NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PG#hasComeFromMpArticle=true#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PG#hasComeFromMpArticle=true#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\" target=\"_blank\">PG</a>) back in October 2024. More specifically, I published an <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4725230-procter-and-gamble-buy-the-dip\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4725230-procter-and-gamble-buy-the-dip\" target=\"_blank\">article</a> on 10-5-2024 under the title of \"Procter &amp; Gamble: Buy The Dip\u201d on Seeking Alpha. As you</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157198425/image_157198425.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745450-procter-and-gamble-inventory-does-not-lie-and-points-to-hold", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 02:52:51"}, {"id": "4745456", "title": "The Yen Weakens As The BoJ Holds", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Close up image of Japanese Yen on a white background\" data-id=\"109835538\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">gaffera</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Min Joo Kang, Senior Economist, South Korea and Japan and Chris Turner, Global Head of Markets and Regional Head of Research for UK &amp; CEE</em></p> <p></p> <h2>A January hike is not a done deal, says Ueda</h2> <p>According to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/109835538/image_109835538.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745456-yen-weakens-as-boj-holds", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 02:50:00"}, {"id": "4745451", "title": "Super Micro Computer's Outlook Is Now A PIPE Dream", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Fortunes Lost: Winning Lottery Destroyed by Spill\" data-id=\"157501967\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1022px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Saturated/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>GenAI has created incredible opportunities for companies to globally benefit from surging productivity gains and unlocking efficiency. As a result, organizations have demonstrated strong ambitions in investing in and upgrading their technology infrastructure to support</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157501967/image_157501967.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745451-super-micro-computer-smci-outlook-is-now-a-pipe-dream", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 02:15:59"}, {"id": "4745446", "title": "Rexel SA Facing Challenges, But The Macro Environment Should Be Near The Bottom", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151912557/image_2151912557.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Electrician fixing a fuse box at a house\" data-id=\"2151912557\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"971px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151912557/image_2151912557.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151912557/image_2151912557.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151912557/image_2151912557.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151912557/image_2151912557.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151912557/image_2151912557.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151912557/image_2151912557.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151912557/image_2151912557.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151912557/image_2151912557.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Hispanolistic/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The last six or so months haven\u2019t been the easiest for French electrical products distributor <strong>Rexel SA </strong>(<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RXEEY\" title=\"Rexel S.A.\">OTCPK:RXEEY</a>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RXLSF\" title=\"Rexel S.A.\">OTCPK:RXLSF</a>). Higher rates have hurt activity in both residential and non-residential construction, and industrial sales have been hit by not</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2151912557/image_2151912557.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745446-rexel-sa-facing-challenges-but-the-macro-environment-should-be-near-the-bottom", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 01:47:39"}, {"id": "4745443", "title": "CAVA: Excellent Same Store Sales Growth Tempered By Ridiculous Price (Rating Upgrade)", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212709124/image_1212709124.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Men eating Greek Salad\" data-id=\"1212709124\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212709124/image_1212709124.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212709124/image_1212709124.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212709124/image_1212709124.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212709124/image_1212709124.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212709124/image_1212709124.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212709124/image_1212709124.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212709124/image_1212709124.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212709124/image_1212709124.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">JulPo/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>AI software isn't the only sector having a big moment in 2024. Fast-casual restaurant chains, especially those targeting a healthier demographic, are also skyrocketing to new heights in 2024. Sweetgreen (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SG\" title=\"Sweetgreen, Inc.\">SG</a>) and CAVA (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CAVA\" title=\"CAVA Group, Inc.\">CAVA</a></span>) have each seen</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1212709124/image_1212709124.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745443-cava-excellent-same-store-sales-growth-tempered-by-ridiculous-price-upgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 01:35:45"}, {"id": "4745441", "title": "Enerpac Tool Group Stock Takes A Dive On Q1 Earnings", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Labourers Planning on Site\" data-id=\"1917054502\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">FatCamera</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>December 18th was a rough day for shareholders of <b>Enerpac Tool Group Corp.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/EPAC\" title=\"Enerpac Tool Group Corp.\">EPAC</a></span>). As the broader market plunged following <a href=\"https://www.npr.org/2024/12/18/nx-s1-5230508/federal-reserve-interest-rates-economy-inflation\" rel=\"nofollow\">news</a> that the Federal Reserve would likely only be cutting interest rates twice next year</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1917054502/image_1917054502.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745441-enerpac-tool-group-stock-takes-a-dive-on-q1-earnings", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 01:26:46"}, {"id": "4745440", "title": "Dividend Growers Hedge Against Trump Bump To Inflation", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Money growth\" data-id=\"1445810162\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1055px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>By Michael Clarfeld, CFA</p> <p>Portfolio Manager, ClearBridge Investments</p> <h2>There Will Be Second-Order Effects to Trump 2.0</h2> <p>Trump won \u2014 buy crypto! Trump won \u2014 buy energy stocks! Trump won and will loosen regulations on financial companies \u2014 buy bank stocks!</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745440-dividend-growers-hedge-against-trump-bump-to-inflation", "pub_date": "2024-12-20 01:07:31"}]}